article.headline: Oral Roberts 72, Florida A&amp,M 51
article.story: CANCUN, Mexico -- Dominique Morrison scored 19 points and Kevin Ford had 11 points and 12 rebounds as Oral Roberts beat Florida A&M 72-51 Wednesday in the Cancun Challenge at the Moon Palace Resort. Freshman Warren Niles added 15 points and four assists for the Golden Eagles (3-3). He was 6-of-8 from the floor and 3-for-4 on 3-pointers. David Buchanon led the Rattlers (0-6) with 14 points on 5-of-7 shooting. The rest of his Florida A&M teammates were a combined 15 of 64, as Oral Roberts held the Rattlers to 28 percent shooting.
